    "en": {
      "title": "Minister's Notification on Petrol",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekara has said that supply shortages have been rectified and more fuel stocks have been distributed in the last 4 days.",
        "He said the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation storage terminal would continue to supply 4000 metric tons of diesel and 3000 metric tons of gasoline daily.",
        "Also, the minister mentioned that 35,000 metric tons of 92 grade petrol will be landed today and night."
      ],
